        <p>Learn with friends in groups of 4–8. A fun, social way to improve your game. Perfect for beginners and intermediate players.</p>
        <div class="price-tag">From £25 / person</div>
        <a href="/book?activity=group-lesson" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Book Now</a>
      </div>
      <div class="content-card">
        <div class="content-card-icon"><i class="ri-user-star-line"></i></div>
        <h3>Junior Academy</h3>
        <p>Ages 6–16. Weekly sessions designed to develop young talent through structured coaching with fun challenges and competitions.</p>
        <div class="price-tag">From £20 / session</div>
        <a href="/book?activity=junior-academy" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Book Now</a>
      </div>
      <div class="content-card">
        <div class="content-card-icon"><i class="ri-vidicon-line"></i></div>
        <h3>Video Analysis</h3>
        <p>High-speed camera swing analysis to identify and correct faults. Includes before-and-after comparison and takeaway drills.</p>
        <div class="price-tag">From £60 / session</div>
        <a href="/book?activity=video-analysis" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Book Now</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section alt-bg">
    <h2 class="section-heading">WHY LEARN WITH US?</h2>
    <div class="features-row">
      <div class="feature-item">
        <i class="ri-medal-line"></i>
        <h4>PGA Certified</h4>
        <p>All our instructors are PGA-qualified professionals</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <i class="ri-line-chart-line"></i>
        <h4>TopTracer Tech</h4>
        <p>Real-time ball flight data for measurable improvement</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <i class="ri-calendar-check-line"></i>
        <h4>Flexible Scheduling</h4>
        <p>Morning, afternoon and evening slots available 7 days a week</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <i class="ri-shield-check-line"></i>
        <h4>Satisfaction Guaranteed</h4>
        <p>Not happy? Rebook for free with another instructor</p>
      </div>
    </div>
